    "The calculation is shown in Eq.",
    "(3) CER = S + D + I N.",
    "Summary of Chinese DSR approaches, include including dialect category, method description, and accuracy Assuming that the word sequences and transcription sequences are consistent, S denotes the number of errors in the replaced words, D denotes the number of deleted words, I indicates the inserted dialect words, and N represents the sum of words.",
